<item>
  <title>Drupal community, please meet Vijay</title>
  <link>http://janezurevc.name/drupal-community-please-meet-vijay</link>
  <description>
&lt;span&gt;Drupal community, please meet Vijay&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;&lt;span lang="" about="http://janezurevc.name/users/slashrsm" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" xml:lang=""&gt;slashrsm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;Tue, 24.05.2016 - 10:40&lt;/span&gt;

            &lt;div class="field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field--item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://groups.drupal.org/node/510665"&gt;Google summer of code 2016&lt;/a&gt; started with a full swing this week. &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/isthegeek"&gt;Vijay&lt;/a&gt; is one of the students participating in it. He is working on the Media module for Drupal 8.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;He wrote &lt;a href="https://isthegeek.svbtle.com/gsoc-16-with-drupal"&gt;an introduction blog post&lt;/a&gt;. I'd like to invite you to read it, say hi and follow his work as it progresses through the summer.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Welcome in the Drupal community Vijay!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      
